messageBody:
The way recommended by Yahoo! Groups, where this mailing list is hosted, is
to send an email to the special address
junit-unsubscribe@yahoogroups.comand that will take care of it. At the
bottom of each message that you
receive from this list is a clickable link (if you read you read your email
in a halfway modern reader) that will generate the correct email for you.

Simon
(One of the JUnit mailing list moderators)
